Walden Bello, a socialist candidate for the Philippine Senate, files a petition that may disqualify boxer Manny Pacquiao for violating election rules regarding publicity. Based on the commission's rules, Pacquiao's wife, Jinkee Pacquiao, may substitute. (Rappler), (The New York Times), (Fox Sports)President-elect Donald Trump names South Carolina governor Nikki Haley as United States Ambassador to the United Nations. (BBC)